l have no problem with that.

105
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:15,800
l,... tell me about yourself.

106
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,120
Myself?

107
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:20,000
Your hopes,
your dreams.

108
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:24,760
Are you married? Obviously not
or it wouldn't be ''Miss Fitzgerald''.

109
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,960
Do you have a boyfriend?

110
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:29,200
ls this why you got me here?

111
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,880
l just,...

112
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:35,760
What's your life like?
Do you have any hobbies?

113
