l have a meeting
in 1 5 minutes, so...

114
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:43,840
Your marital status is none
of my business.

115
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:46,400
Maybe it's a touchy point
with you.

116
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:48,920
