which end is up.

143
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:22,520
ln your case,
it would be hard to tell.

144
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:25,360
Don't see me out.
Someone may think we're together.

145
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:27,080
Do l look like
an organ grinder?

146
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,640
