00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:57,440
-C.W., ever been to Paris?
-l've never been out of the country.

207
00:12:57,760 --> 00:12:59,600
Six-zero-dash-six...

208
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,760
eight-dash-five...

209
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:03,920
eight-five-seven.

210
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:06,920
That's right.
That's exactly correct.

211
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:13,800
And now for something l call
''The Power of Jade Scorpion''.

212
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:18,160
