234
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:33,200
Betty Ann Fitzgerald.
l also work at North Coast.

235
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:35,200
So you work together?

236
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:38,040
l can't stand her.

237
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:39,960
Don't pay attention to him.

238
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:43,640
He's a sleazy megalomaniac who's
frightened of women.

239
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,440
Enough. Sleep.

240
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,160
Silence.

241
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:53,320
The Jade Scorpion wants
you to go to the deepest level.

242
00:14:54,760 --> 00:14:58,880
When l say ''Constantinople'', you'll
drop into the deepest trance.

